describe.a: A fun and occasionally challenging game. The goal was to draw lines to route a ball to fall into a cup.

approach.q: What was your overarching approach to solve each level?
approach.a: Defend the sides of the cup as much as possible, keep the lines slope as similar as possible.

issues.a: One level I needed 4 attempts, felt like the ball was stopping for no reason. Either way I was able to complete it!
